{"tid":1385924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今集劉細良唔駛認真聽 佢只係自保","createTime":"2019-07-30T08:03:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T13:17:08.000Z","uid":78068,"like":202,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"7c1cf2bc3e0974135af8aca9034a1860b7ba35df","tid":1385924,"uid":78068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:03:07.000Z","msg":"無大台運動唔駛捧神 呢啲基本唔駛講啦<br />\n另外如果大家有留心聽今集城寨 就會發現<br />\n佢嘅「建議」及「評論」只係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">保護緊自己</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n- 成集佢不斷暗示明示自己畀人擺上枱，不下三次強調自己唔係大台唔係軍師。<br />\n<br />\n- 亦表明自己感到受威脅 甚至因而臨時決定取消元朗之行<br />\n<br />\n因此佢作出咗以下回應嚟強調自己清白：<br />\n<br />\n- 最明顯就係鼓吹<span style=\"color: gold;\">終止勇武</span> 就算下星期再衝擊 都可以保障此運動非因其分析所致<br />\n<br />\n- 一邊話呢場運動係存在主義運動，一邊<span style=\"color: violet;\">計算「值唔值得」</span>去下「停勇武」嘅結論<br />\n<br />\n- 表明自己由始至終都係和理非 甚至時至今日都覺得唔應該打爛立會玻璃，再三<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">強調自己「反對暴力」</span><br />\n<br />\n- 甚至否定721後勇武行動，形容示威者被射爆頭遠不及警黑一事震撼721後行動只屬徒勞<br />\n<br />\n- 提供多個資料來源，元朗共和國只係網絡笑話⋯⋯多次提到<span style=\"color: red;\">連登</span>⋯⋯強調content 非佢create<br />\n<br />\n- 提及示威者可憐，從而解釋自己出現中上環只因同情而非認同衝擊行為<br />\n<br />\n- 宣揚和理非上場，如港澳辦昨日所講，和平遊行可以繼續，但要終止暴力，跟足guideline<br />\n<br />\n- 將五大訴求集中，甚至<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">減少</span></span>至「成立獨立調查委員會」，最多大眾共識，連最有錢班商會都同意嘅訴求，如政府集中只派呢一粒糖畀你，有起碼一半和理非都會收貨，運動將無以為繼。<br />\n<br />\n- 表明時勢做英雄，非其有獨特之處，只係大家想搵評論聽<br />\n<br />\n其實唔止，仲有好多細微處。<br />\n總之佢今集只係將自己涉事程度減到最低，唔駛認真採用。<br />\n<br />\n無大台就唔好造神，資訊自己判斷消化<br />\n有啲嘢係事實\b，例如美國已經出賣咗香港。<br />\n歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df3e506b03668168d6fd89b6a9dec8fd92ad677f","tid":1385924,"uid":39181,"like":8,"dislike":68,"score":-60,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:05:55.000Z","msg":"勇武既回合已經結束，係時候要交畀和理非"},{"pid":"538165310ee66ed404969eef5a528e79d5c405f5","tid":1385924,"uid":215876,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"df3e506b03668168d6fd89b6a9dec8fd92ad677f","tid":1385924,"uid":39181,"like":8,"dislike":68,"score":-60,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:05:55.000Z","msg":"勇武既回合已經結束，係時候要交畀和理非"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:09:18.000Z","msg":"唔見得係"},{"pid":"7ab1fdfb3dbc461cee0b1754bb641f51d0d9bb88","tid":1385924,"uid":1086,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:12:03.000Z","msg":"差佬冇後顧之憂<br />\n仲想同差佬硬碰硬,唔會阻止<br />\n但你們鼓吹上前線打既考慮吓自己賠唔賠得返個仔俾人地老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0967f135a33e66e68a651065481f5c3927104a4","tid":1385924,"uid":81996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:13:05.000Z","msg":"討論下"},{"pid":"0939069c542c566f92f961a9c67f55598a123a0e","tid":1385924,"uid":196430,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:13:25.000Z","msg":"明架啦，同今年主場新聞一樣姐"},{"pid":"5bc627967629da6fb3d540867969267855f5926b","tid":1385924,"uid":196430,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"0939069c542c566f92f961a9c67f55598a123a0e","tid":1385924,"uid":196430,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:13:25.000Z","msg":"明架啦，同今年主場新聞一樣姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:13:38.000Z","msg":"當年"},{"pid":"f33a6520f5e739725f20e91ac0d248b44d277794","tid":1385924,"uid":72000,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:17:08.000Z","msg":"for reference and suggestion only<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a4fab21c8dcc477e2f0f0855331ab90ed5f0180","tid":1385924,"uid":78068,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"f33a6520f5e739725f20e91ac0d248b44d277794","tid":1385924,"uid":72000,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:17:08.000Z","msg":"for reference and suggestion only<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:18:59.000Z","msg":"態度正確<br />\n主要係見好多連登仔追住真係當軍師<br />\n唔係要否定佢講嘅嘢<br />\n而係了解多啲點解佢會講呢啲嘢"},{"pid":"a19bea93011f343a51360371f0c11232fd8ddb6e","tid":1385924,"uid":55851,"like":8,"dislike":39,"score":-31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:20:30.000Z","msg":"聽得出佢好淆底，懦夫一條，以後唔會再聽"},{"pid":"25a0f0be148df05b128489124a919bbff30d8054","tid":1385924,"uid":22898,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:20:40.000Z","msg":"以戰論戰，理性，非割席。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得佢某程度有道理，依加既勇武最大問題係無清晰目標。<br />\n<br />\n例如71，入立法會宣言係目標。726入機場宣傳係目標。咁達成目標即可散。<br />\n<br />\n但係依加前線無清晰目標，一味留守同推進，而警察有無限物資同人力補充，長期做落去都唔係辦法。<br />\n<br />\n我唔係唔同意勇武，但係會唔會定一個較清楚既目標去做。<br />\n<br />\n就算假設勇武可以打低曬前線班狗，破佢地防線都好，破完之後又要點做？依個問題一定要諗，其實都係繼續守，繼續推，最後變持久戰，破左之後人地可以再補充，再設防。"},{"pid":"c60f28115909ae32c9c24111852cfff24d18ab2c","tid":1385924,"uid":72000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a4fab21c8dcc477e2f0f0855331ab90ed5f0180","tid":1385924,"uid":78068,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"f33a6520f5e739725f20e91ac0d248b44d277794","tid":1385924,"uid":72000,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:17:08.000Z","msg":"for reference and suggestion only<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:18:59.000Z","msg":"態度正確<br />\n主要係見好多連登仔追住真係當軍師<br />\n唔係要否定佢講嘅嘢<br />\n而係了解多啲點解佢會講呢啲嘢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:21:06.000Z","msg":"最緊要係共識一致<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67527c7e286e90dbe04101fe2f2de9926aa3a8f8","tid":1385924,"uid":276684,"like":21,"dislike":5,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:21:17.000Z","msg":"啱聽就係神<br />\n唔啱聽就係鬼<br />\n佔中就係咁樣散"},{"pid":"dd78858889877147343bd15d08eeb9eb825f33af","tid":1385924,"uid":36901,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:22:17.000Z","msg":"聽得出去感受到威脅<br />\n有啲嘢唔使講出口都知道發生緊乜事啦"},{"pid":"f9599353e9237cb8c49f7f4ffe4bd9a005a7191f","tid":1385924,"uid":49316,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:23:01.000Z","msg":"棒打出頭鳥。你估佢唔驚  支共黑暗手段乜都做得出 佢前幾個星期已經預告佐<br />\n<br />\n黨報出聲關懷 一定有後續 明既揾幾政府部門搞下去擋野。暗既揾中間人嚇下<br />\n<br />\n不過引證佢前幾集分析正確。宜家佢同19才子都叫中場休息。我相信呢個係支共想法。和理非可比繼續  唔俾衝擊<br />\n<br />\n無勇武撚 運動一早已散 但個個星期有幾十義士俾位唔係辦法 可以諗下<br />\n<br />\n接遊學 呢個對一D人係有阻嚇作用<br />\n快閃示威 打消耗戰<br />\n繼續攬抄巴行動。要求外國制裁高官黑警<br />\nIT9. 成立中央黑警黒材料 大數據庫 加起底 永久存案 到獨立調查有用<br />\n<br />\n大家加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5ac724593e0350330965f13e2e747ff7559249b","tid":1385924,"uid":128522,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"df3e506b03668168d6fd89b6a9dec8fd92ad677f","tid":1385924,"uid":39181,"like":8,"dislike":68,"score":-60,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:05:55.000Z","msg":"勇武既回合已經結束，係時候要交畀和理非"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:23:29.000Z","msg":"唔係回合結束,<br />\n<br />\n只係跟住呢星期和理非打牌頭<br />\n勇武要暗底儲氣, 儲裝, 同埋玩下除暴GO"},{"pid":"d6665c5e77531800149930608a5f8999df4fa256","tid":1385924,"uid":24140,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"538165310ee66ed404969eef5a528e79d5c405f5","tid":1385924,"uid":215876,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"df3e506b03668168d6fd89b6a9dec8fd92ad677f","tid":1385924,"uid":39181,"like":8,"dislike":68,"score":-60,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:05:55.000Z","msg":"勇武既回合已經結束，係時候要交畀和理非"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:09:18.000Z","msg":"唔見得係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:23:53.000Z","msg":"準備將軍澳啦"},{"pid":"cd8c7d7f326cff591758680e4549fc57ed5ad5a4","tid":1385924,"uid":28155,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:23:58.000Z","msg":"捉鬼個時就咁撚威"},{"pid":"5a1b44987e27505667950e4838c50fb1e41df902","tid":1385924,"uid":189799,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:27:38.000Z","msg":"勇武和理各有各做。<br />\n唔係唔好勇武，不過要改變玩法，唔好728咁送頭。"},{"pid":"7110ff2c2340628af69a9a4de504