tedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:02:12.000Z","msg":"我覺得唔使每次都勇武<br />\n有目標突擊先出發<br />\n無就和平散去<br />\n唔好再玩留守"},{"pid":"6af03932c895b7754122e905bd94d3965f7a8d0e","tid":1385924,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5ac724593e0350330965f13e2e747ff7559249b","tid":1385924,"uid":128522,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"df3e506b03668168d6fd89b6a9dec8fd92ad677f","tid":1385924,"uid":39181,"like":8,"dislike":68,"score":-60,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:05:55.000Z","msg":"勇武既回合已經結束，係時候要交畀和理非"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:23:29.000Z","msg":"唔係回合結束,<br />\n<br />\n只係跟住呢星期和理非打牌頭<br />\n勇武要暗底儲氣, 儲裝, 同埋玩下除暴GO"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:03:57.000Z","msg":"你明唔明咩係回合<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一人一round"},{"pid":"499549be6000d90aeee7baf512868948f9473d49","tid":1385924,"uid":122672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:14:25.000Z","msg":"係老塗捧佢做戰耙<br />\n理性過老蕭少少既Kol"},{"pid":"4edc00985ae59b9298ca76559673e8aa51b24353","tid":1385924,"uid":2036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:16:24.000Z","msg":"佢唔想上位有佢思量<br />\n我地亦唔係要推佢上 呢點係一致<br />\n<br />\n佢既對口係和理非應該點做 應該點幫<br />\n<br />\n佢話唔勇武 亦都有原因係728 太慘烈 大家士氣都受損都要回氣<br />\n<br />\n呢個星期先解決被捕/聲援被捕 識人既 知道身邊有人奶野既 幫手搵律師<br />\n<br />\n和理非睇下做到幾多野先再考慮<br />\n<br />\n對面武裝係728 再提升 仲有水炮未出<br />\n盲撞只會再傷我方攻力"},{"pid":"dfcfa9b1224f5513da4f52cf1098864fb8508dd3","tid":1385924,"uid":90692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:21:52.000Z","msg":"真係唔覺喎， 未必個個都會認同曬佢講法，但係我又感覺唔到呢啲小人之心。<br />\n可能勇武點都會對和理非有抗拒。<br />\n 但係到今時今日嘅勇武回合，除左不斷送頭 犧牲手足，仲可以有咩突破？<br />\n<br />\n我老豆反而係聽完今集終於接受到勇武嘅人。"},{"pid":"85e74dc480f95eddccb527d60cf673ef598e310d","tid":1385924,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:23:18.000Z","msg":"軟維穩"},{"pid":"edd4fe44182b0b057fcb9f0c36abc73abdbcde28","tid":1385924,"uid":90692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:23:23.000Z","msg":"只有罷工同智取係出路，如果唔係一星期都可以整死晒啲人啦。"},{"pid":"757770d69a589f23679ca86af57d5ec51d7ad232","tid":1385924,"uid":90692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67527c7e286e90dbe04101fe2f2de9926aa3a8f8","tid":1385924,"uid":276684,"like":21,"dislike":5,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:21:17.000Z","msg":"啱聽就係神<br />\n唔啱聽就係鬼<br />\n佔中就係咁樣散"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:24:01.000Z","msg":"雨傘係互割割散"},{"pid":"0e640f813a426de4ca4be0ab12f2dc716b1940d6","tid":1385924,"uid":196535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:25:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da7dac9239becf47fc92b7ba99ab9b9fc48ec4e9","tid":1385924,"uid":199235,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:27:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UXK73qb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUXK73qb.jpg&h=13edf13e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自從知道大家要涯住餓咁去對抗，又睇到黑警既不對等暴力，再睇埋呢張圖真係喊左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家雖然仲有一團火同鬥志，但有邊個唔想有大人保護同支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大人既世界係好難會叫佢地出黎幫我地擋子彈，但佢地就可以用另一種方式保護出黎抗爭既大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n劉細良雖然係自保，但唔係無道理<br />\n<br />\n721咁大衝擊後，727,728，抗爭者再涯幾多子彈同催淚彈，焦點都係圍繞721黑幫打人，所謂邊際利潤遞減，大家只會開始適應黑警既無理暴力，之後既工作可能係事倍功半，要得到外界更大反應，可能要流更多血，被拉被鎖，甚至有人死亡，我真係唔忍心見到咁既情況出現<br />\n<br />\n雖然咁講其實勇武派已經十分之成功做到佢地既目標<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就係向全世界揭露中共一國兩制既謊言，警黑合作，仲有最後727對黑勢力既唔容忍，已經非常成功。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n故此，勇武派短期目標已經120%超額完成，係下一個目標前不如暫時休息，等全香港肯企出黎既其他市民幫你好嗎？"},{"pid":"d0dcdc2ae6761c6786ae192bec34076b32ccc9cb","tid":1385924,"uid":209609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:32:38.000Z","msg":"佢人在加拿大，保護咩？"},{"pid":"3fa8bd91a576ba309545a72345f46283ad63fa1a","tid":1385924,"uid":78068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da7dac9239becf47fc92b7ba99ab9b9fc48ec4e9","tid":1385924,"uid":199235,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:27:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UXK73qb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUXK73qb.jpg&h=13edf13e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自從知道大家要涯住餓咁去對抗，又睇到黑警既不對等暴力，再睇埋呢張圖真係喊左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><